    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gardens often provided with shade, flowing water, pavilions, and elaborate plantings for private enjoyment; common in Islamic countries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
